{"tid":1444760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"＜又到中秋＞文宣係時候大家重溫月餅嘅抗暴起源","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:11:10.000Z","uid":277511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97a288742529a66dc17cbde7c65a33f9f111c05b","tid":1444760,"uid":277511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人們買了月餅回到家中，發覺裏面藏着紙條，上面寫着：「中秋夜，殺韃子，迎義軍!」 於是眾人紛紛起義反抗統治者，中秋節吃月餅的習俗就是這樣留下來的。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/lxgo6m9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2Flxgo6m9.html&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=042c10c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/lxgo6m9.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkedcity.net/sch_files/a/phc/phc-cic/public_html/MoonCake.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkedcity.net%2Fsch_files%2Fa%2Fphc%2Fphc-cic%2Fpublic_html%2FMoonCake.htm&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=73d1e665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkedcity.net/sch_files/a/phc/phc-cic/public_html/MoonCake.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n今個中秋，係時候請權貴派吃月餅了。"}]}